{"tid":1691384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸已經有恐怖分子滲透香港","createTime":"2019-11-03T15:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T05:18:51.000Z","uid":8477,"like":806,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":137,"replies":[{"pid":"2a2766fb3654997f16ab4b0c17fc01d86630a72e","tid":1691384,"uid":8477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:40:45.000Z","msg":"我講緊嘅唔係黑警，唔係解放軍，而係真真正正由中央政府雇用嘅恐怖分子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我地可以點做？<br />\n<br />\n我建議每次出現大陸恐怖分子，千祈唔好私了，但係萬一佢唔小心仆親跌到手手腳腳都斷撚曬，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">然後打開佢電話通訊APP，再影低全部可疑群組嘅contact list</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n就算contact list入面無我地要嘅線索，至少可以瓦解佢地嘅行動，雖知佢地重新步署都要時間<br />\n<br />\n再唔係，當加多幾個名入制裁名單都無壞"},{"pid":"b55fd0b1d6e5d3479bb5c2dff92a2cbf3a5c2916","tid":1691384,"uid":297569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"望大家嚟睇下 時刻保持冷靜同分析能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［警世］唔好咁易受風向影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"81a6c74eece4222d971303e8d8d98748c853fce6","tid":1691384,"uid":8477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:47:38.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"e0f4431fb08083fc2f4049e9b6021cd84ee85e12","tid":1691384,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78bceaefff1a9f818493211803d8719659f8aa1","tid":1691384,"uid":37413,"like":111,"dislike":1,"score":110,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:51:41.000Z","msg":"都唔知第幾次支那狗出刀斬人<br />\n上次劏肚腸斬出埋嗰位手足唔知點"},{"pid":"88f05830c88ddf6e9a8016697ee6bb89b6ef3bd7","tid":1691384,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff05b9a936a7ef3ff40b417ac6efd354054f79b2","tid":1691384,"uid":51814,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FhtZgyf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhtZgyf.jpg&h=7cd7fd3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人，醒下啦！<br />\n香港警察已經被完全洗腦，<br />\n當所有反政府嘅市民唔係人，<br />\n係曱甴，係害蟲，係低等生物。<br />\n唔好再浪費時間同佢地講道理，講人性。<br />\n唔好再冒被捕嘅險去撚狗發洩心中怒氣。<br />\n唔好再期望佢會回復以前嘅專業。<br />\n唔好再理會佢開記者會狡辯自己。<br />\n香港警察已經壽終正寢，已經被解散咗，<br />\n而家只係由中共控制住嘅政治劊子手。</span>"},{"pid":"a9c5e437c457808af127ba31ae5d5d992a428f2e","tid":1691384,"uid":331973,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:53:46.000Z","msg":"太古條友戰鬥力好高"},{"pid":"46abad55a568f1c099303f58e75cd3b8a3d6e380","tid":1691384,"uid":8477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"09681ca36d93537ac3787b7b50618653d4b3e3b2","tid":1691384,"uid":108813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:54:59.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"8e42ea4e302a527a6544370f8cf7f9025453adba","tid":1691384,"uid":173072,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">手㬹 - 諗下折木條動作係點, 自己諗下應該點做<br />\n手腕 - 試下自己左手手腕順時針方向轉到盡, 右手手腕逆時針方向轉到盡, 係乜感覺, 如果有人呢個時候大力扭多下會點?<br />\n手肩膀 - 呢個難度高D, 試下伸直隻手, 向背向上, 好似要掂另一隻手ge肩膀, 係咪唔得呢? 諗下伸直隻手, 要向另一隻手方向好似支棒咁推, 可以用埋身體重量加埋支重力點, 咁個重點(肩膀) 會點呢?</span>"},{"pid":"5087faa03c0847da8ca0d0ce401a2cf4e9fc1145","tid":1691384,"uid":158499,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{